metadata.name: Labelled Space Edition: Tote Bag #1
metadata.description: Labelled is an upcoming brand and the ‘World’s First Phygital Concept Store’. Their Space Edition features a unique tote bag that unlocks an NFT through a physical backed token, offering customers a groundbreaking shopping experience that combines physical and digital elements. The product design is inspired by 'The Wandering Earth' novel, featuring an uncracked binary code on the tote bag which adds a futuristic and playful element, appealing to fans of science fiction and those who appreciate unique and unconventional designs. Labelled's innovative approach to blending physical and digital experiences sets them apart in the retail industry, creating new possibilities for customer engagement and digital ownership.
